# Smart Animation

## Usage

```elixir
Mix.install([{:kino, github: "livebook-dev/kino"}, {:smart_animation, path: "."}])
```

```elixir
defmodule Counter do
  use GenServer

  def start_link(_) do
    GenServer.start_link(__MODULE__, [], name: __MODULE__)
  end

  def init(_) do
    send(self(), :increment)
    {:ok, 0}
  end

  def handle_info(:increment, state) do
    Process.sleep(1000)
    send(self(), :increment)
    {:noreply, state + 1}
  end
end

{:ok, counter_pid} = Counter.start_link([])
```

